    "description": "<p>Welcome to ICHIGO.SG (一起购),your one-stop-shop for all your needs. Our mission is to provide our customers with a wide range of high-quality products at competitive prices, coupled with exceptional customer service and reliable shipping.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We operate primarily through Facebook Live Streaming (https://www.facebook.com/sg.ichigo), integrated with our ecommerce website, which will be designed to provide a seamless user experience for customers. We understand the importance of convenience, and that's why we have created a user-friendly website that makes shopping online a breeze, during our Live Stream and at our ecommerce store.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>At ICHIGO.SG, we take pride in offering a wide range of products that are carefully curated to meet the needs of our customers. Whether you're looking for authentic food, latest fashion, high quality skin &amp;body care, health &amp; wellness, niche collectibles, reliable home appliances, or trendy household products, we have you covered.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Thank you for choosing ICHIGO.SG as your trusted online retailer. We look forward to serving you for years to come, let’s 一起购!</p>",
